{"tid":1520050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」希望勇武聽日冷靜，10月1日 先係大戰","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:27:57.000Z","uid":19092,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6c2381e995186d02dc24bc02de8cacec9cd0fb","tid":1520050,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"佢想引晒你地出去，打死晒你地咋。 <br />\n林鄭愈唔想拖就愈要慢慢同佢玩野， 冇必要同班差佬決戰。 <br />\n<br />\n我就住中西區某警署對面， 佢地尋日已經set 左好多器材同佈緊防。 <br />\n<br />\n人地真係設定左個局黎捉你地。 <br />\n<br />\n你問我，佢唔比你遊行你偏偏要去， 岩。 但係唔係明知幾千人伏你地都去送死。<br />\n<br />\n西區有d 親中人士， 上星期已經放風叫831 唔做生意唔送貨， 因為我直接有張單話要改日期， 條友7日前已經話831 可能死人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30c85f58e640ec681abd5397ae59d5c05e6a9a6","tid":1520050,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=d53c5136\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=bc3c049a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=4b3ce95f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"0e9812e6df01e1866ae89af77ce5775ccb140f9e","tid":1520050,"uid":60310,"like":0,"dislike